N of_IN the_DT National_NNP Soccer_NNP Hall_NNP of_IN Fame_NNP Alexander Alec Wood  June 12 1907 in Lochgelly Scotland  July 20 1987 in Gary Indiana Was a former Scottish American soccer defender footballdefender  Wood began his club career in the United States before moving to England in the early 1930s  He also played all three US games at the 1930 FIFA World Cup  He is a member of the National Soccer Hall of Fame